{"tid":881314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港，音樂人先係真正意義上嘅離地撚","createTime":"2018-10-29T10:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T01:05:45.000Z","uid":93273,"like":26,"dislike":200,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"23ba5fbc187007c39c23ba42f69e238524866c2a","tid":881314,"uid":93273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"講緊真係音樂學院讀出嚟嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n離地唔係淨係指收入，係計埋生活品質<br />\n<br />\n一個鐘至少搵400，weekday通常番兩三個鐘工，日日可以訓到十一二點，係禮拜六日先忙啲教六個鐘，但永遠唔會有no pay OT，咁嘅工時已經講緊搵 30k 一個月，仲要收入幾多任佢自己報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔係搵得超多，但工時係我三份一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有connection 嘅，一個月都至少一兩個event 表演，咁又執多幾千，有啲做埋演唱會live band嘅搵得仲勁<br />\n<br />\n番工做嘅嘢係自己興趣，又好少受氣<br />\n<br />\n最離地係個社會好似真係唔關佢哋事咁，永遠唔會撞中番工放工peak hour，閒日放假，假日番工，政府亂咁洗錢又傷唔到佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  除咗買樓做唔到mortgage，佢哋生活真係超自由<br />\n<br />\n見到以前幾個夾開樂團嘅師兄嘅生活，我真係好後悔中學嗰時點解咁聽老母話，信音樂搵唔到食，走咗去讀BBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff12b1d38f8b065b344fe20953951705c65726a6","tid":881314,"uid":65530,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4592ad9f31c2b87694b196c4ff7e569abd8cb202","tid":881314,"uid":84613,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"真係識教keep到學生先係，都有好多生活過得好霉"},{"pid":"c94399f5654dd93bdb4fba351cc8013a1ab185c8","tid":881314,"uid":122592,"like":106,"dislike":3,"score":103,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:59:35.000Z